snippet.title: The Stuff You Need to Be Considered a Real Adult (feat. Judy Gold) - You Up w/ Nikki Glaser
snippet.description:
Judy Gold, Anya Marina and Andrew Collin chat with Nikki about their living habits, and Judy intervenes in Andrew’s messy lifestyle.  

About You Up w/ Nikki Glaser:  
Nikki Glaser and her sidekick Andrew Collin host You Up w/ Nikki Glaser on Comedy Central Radio, SiriusXM Ch. 95, Monday through Thursday at 10AM ET/7AM PT.
